    {
      "id": "radial-menu-overview",
      "type": "markdown",
      "label": "Radial Menu",
      "position": {
        "x": 700,
        "y": -900
      },
      "width": 560,
      "height": 260,
      "visible": true,
      "showLabel": true,
      "data": {
        "markdown": "# Radial Menu\n\nDesign a radial interaction surface for the highest-frequency Twilite actions.\n\nThe goal is not novelty. The goal is to reduce toolbar sprawl while making fast actions feel more spatial and direct.\n\n## First Ring Grammar\n\nThe first circle should be divided into four sections:\n\n- **Layout**\n- **Node Palette**\n- **Info**\n- **Mode**\n\nThat outer grammar should make the menu readable by category before the user has to parse individual actions.",
        "definitionKey": "markdown",
        "_classBinding": {
          "key": "markdown",
          "sourceRef": "/library/classes/nodes/markdown.node-class.node",
          "ref": "/library/classes/nodes/markdown.node-class.node",
          "identity": {
            "graphId": "markdown_class",
            "name": "markdown Node Class",
            "version": "0.1.0",
            "description": "Canonical markdown content node.",
            "createdAt": "2026-02-24T20:05:15Z",
